<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Franciscan University of Steubenville grants credit for successful completion of selected College Board Advanced Placement Examinations. Minimum score accepted is 3 on all exams except Government and Politics of the U.S., which requires a 4.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.franciscan.edu/Catalogs/Undergraduate/" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
